    - target: {fileID: 1180077256920998961, guid: ed1626dd6be01424c9898d47677825bc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[4].lines.Array.size
      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1180077256920998961, guid: ed1626dd6be01424c9898d47677825bc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[5].lines.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1180077256920998961, guid: ed1626dd6be01424c9898d47677825bc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[6].lines.Array.size
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1180077256920998961, guid: ed1626dd6be01424c9898d47677825bc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Sir! Finally, I've been waiting out here for you.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1180077256920998961, guid: ed1626dd6be01424c9898d47677825bc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Graham! Finally, I've been waiting out here for you.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1180077256920998961, guid: ed1626dd6be01424c9898d47677825bc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Yanzie, what's going on?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1180077256920998961, guid: ed1626dd6be01424c9898d47677825bc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: You haven't been to your desk yet, have you?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1180077256920998961, guid: ed1626dd6be01424c9898d47677825bc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: There's a pile of new case files sitting there. And I mean a pile.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1180077256920998961, guid: ed1626dd6be01424c9898d47677825bc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Already? The day hasn't even started.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1180077256920998961, guid: ed1626dd6be01424c9898d47677825bc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[4].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: We've been doing this for years, is that new?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1180077256920998961, guid: ed1626dd6be01424c9898d47677825bc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[4].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: You should hurry and take a look on those case or else you will be late
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1180077256920998961, guid: ed1626dd6be01424c9898d47677825bc, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[5].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Noted. Thanks for the heads up, Yanzie.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
