      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[4].lines.Array.size
      value: 3
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[5].lines.Array.size
      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialogueEntries.Array.data[6].lines.Array.size
      value: 3
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Graham... have you heard?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: There's been a killing in the next town over.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: What happened?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: An old man. Found dead in his own home.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: They're saying his son did it.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: But no one knows why.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: ...A son killing his own father?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[3].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Something doesn't add up.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[4].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: The whole place has gone quiet since it happened.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[4].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: Like the town itself is holding its breath.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[4].lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: Be careful if you're heading there, Graham.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[5].lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: I'll find out what really happened.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[5].lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: I always do.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6600550335227136483, guid: 9d5b11a738b7a81479c746124fec548f, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'dialogueEntries.Array.data[5].lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: Be careful if you're heading there, Graham.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
